overview: NANA MIZUKI LIVE GRACE 2011 ―ORCHESTRA― is Mizuki Nana's thirteenth concert DVD and eightteenth overall video release. DVD & BR containing the NANA MIZUKI LIVE GRACE 2011 ―ORCHESTRA―, held at Yokohama Arena in January 2011 and the Nana Mizuki performance in HIBARY 7 Days. The DVD top the chart at 3 in general and 2 in musical chart. The Bluray version top the Bluray chart at 1.
title: NANA MIZUKI LIVE GRACE 2011 ―ORCHESTRA―
